{"id":"8651","user":{"id":"101860","nickname":"四片叶de三叶吖","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/FqcR23gyTBxqpGDVypZpJe8hw4uq","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"title":"【少院士讲堂】第八课—BOX2.0课程倒计时；第一弹：垂花门","content":"<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;\n<img>\n<img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FhPSbV-ih0rn-M3QGMmTDeFwJzoa\">\n<p>＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝</p>\n<p><font size=\"1\">&nbsp; 作者的话：</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"1\">　　转眼间.......两个月过去了......我们的课程也迎来了最后的倒计时，这些天，我们曾一起成长，学习了各路建筑技巧，也曾一起研究中国建筑：斗拱、牌坊、台基......大家一起建筑，一起进步。要期末考试了，祝大家在期末考出好成绩！&nbsp; &nbsp;</font></p>\n<p>＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝&nbsp; &nbsp; 　　ＨＥＬＬＯ～这里是少院士讲堂，本期我们将建造垂花门，首先让我们先了解一下吧</p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <font size=\"7\">垂&nbsp; 花&nbsp; 门&nbsp;</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"7\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</font><font size=\"6\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</font><font size=\"5\">Daffodil door</font><font size=\"1\" color=\"#c0c0c0\">（强行飙英文）</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"5\">更多图片：</font></p>\n<p><img><font size=\"5\">&nbsp;</font><img></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://img4.imgtn.bdimg.com/it/u=2097441411,2193958345&amp;fm=27&amp;gp=0.jpg\"><br></p>\n<p><font size=\"5\">解析图</font></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://img1.imgtn.bdimg.com/it/u=530296772,49555301&amp;fm=27&amp;gp=0.jpg\">（看不清&nbsp; &nbsp; QWQ&nbsp; &nbsp;）<br></p>\n<p><font size=\"5\">In Minecraft......</font></p>\n<p><img><font size=\"5\"><br></font></p>\n<p>（垂花门）</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><font size=\"5\">名字的由来：</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"5\">&nbsp;</font><font size=\"4\">&nbsp;<img src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/0b/tootha_thumb.gif\">看到这里，大家肯定都会想到，为何名叫垂花门？看下面</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\">&nbsp; </font><font size=\"3\">（相传，在很久以前，有一条黑龙，名叫末.........嗯嗯~不扯了，正解）</font><font size=\"4\">&nbsp;</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\">&nbsp; 垂花门是中国古代建筑院落内部的门，因其檐柱不落地，垂吊在屋檐下，称为垂柱，其下有一垂珠，通常彩绘为花瓣的形式，故被称为垂花门。（小发发<img src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/36/carnation_thumb.gif\">）</font></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><font size=\"5\">简介君已上线：</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"5\">&nbsp;</font><font size=\"4\"><font>&nbsp; 1.</font>垂花门，是四合院中一道很讲究的门，它是内宅与外宅(前院)的分界线和唯一通道。</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\">&nbsp; &nbsp;2.前院与内院用垂花门和院墙相隔。外院多用来接待客人，而内院则是自家人生活起居的地方，外人一般不得随便出入。&nbsp; </font></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\">&nbsp; &nbsp;3.旧时人们常说的“大门不出，二门不迈”，“二门”即指此垂花门。</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\">&nbsp; &nbsp;4. 垂花门是指门上檐柱不落地，而是悬于中柱穿枋上，柱上刻有花瓣联（莲）叶等华丽的木雕，以仰面莲花和花簇头为多。因垂花门的位置在整座宅院的中轴线上，界分内外，建筑华丽，所以，垂花门是全宅中最为醒目的地方。</font></p>\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<p><font size=\"4\">&nbsp; 通过一座小小的垂花门，我们看到的是中国古代劳动人民的勤劳、聪明和智慧，是 一幅幅具有浓郁特色的民俗风情画卷。</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\"><br></font></p>\n<p><font size=\"5\">实际建造：</font><font size=\"2\">（话说，那么大的方块我怎么雕花........）</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\">垂花门：</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\">先起柱+砌墙，&nbsp; 注意我们一直强调的，间隔单数 ！</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\">（嗯，假装柱子上有雕花）</font></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FrCAO-qQWYA77tiWRyKHgAG9T7xx\"><font size=\"4\"><br></font></p>\n<p>构图一下基本型</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FnFjrew7yjHD5WLRAi657lChzeid\"><br></p>\n<p>再进行进一步修改+垂珠</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FmO7Iq027XJn2SutvVAD9E7MzwjD\"><br></p>\n<p>想进去，呵呵，我们是有门槛的&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FjAewUfisyDLO6uQJUpMzLu6K69L\"><br></p>\n<p>感觉垂珠被挡住，默默向前挪一个。+屋脊</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FpIpCLOoSSzP4NdvCDMlj5_bsknN\"><br></p>\n<p>再次微调后的正面照</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/Fn6PH8zvXI_MIcahqVrY9Qb-tLKP\"><br></p>\n<p>上瓦一级准备</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/Fk1DcvyiV40A0DqwK_zNi0gqB32b\"><br></p>\n<p>上瓦ing~</p></p>","board_id":"2","board_name":"积木编程乐园","updated_at":1515848491,"created_at":1515845866,"n_views":538,"n_replies":7,"n_comments":4,"is_authorized":false,"is_featured":true,"is_hotted":false,"is_pinned":false,"tutorial_flag":0,"ask_help_flag":0}